<div class="title">The Devil's Drug</div>
<div class="substance">Caffeine</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Anonymous&Exact=1">Anonymous</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Anonymous. "The Devil's Drug: An Experience with Caffeine (exp14937)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Jun 15, 2007. erowid.org/exp/14937</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right" border="0">
